Subject: drm/amdgpu: wait for IB test on first device open
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 3bfa8897e4d08f822d1d58cf6cbbffbccef82e08
